SIGN IN

Test #1

Steps to reproduce

1. Navigate to https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Enter valid username
3. Enter valid password
4. Click on 'Sign in' button

Expected Result - Home page was opened after successful sign in

Test  №2

Steps to reproduce

1. Navigate to https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Enter invalid username
3. Enter valid password
4. Click on 'Sign in' button

Expected Result - Error message appears after entering invalid credentials

Test #3

1. Navigate to https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Leave input fields with empty values
3. Сlick on 'Sign in' button

 Expected Result - After entering invalid credentials fields are highlighted in red and an error message appears

